high_descs: Walk ahead and turn right and head to the sink.
Pick up the fork out of the sink.
Look up.
Place the fork in the gold cup in the top right cabinet.
Pick up the cup.
Look down at the sink.
Put the cup in the sink to the right of the silverware.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the sink.
Pick up the fork in the sink.
Bring the fork to the cabinet above the sink.
Open the cabinet above the sink and put the fork in the orange cup in the cabinet.
Pick up the orange cup with fork in the cabinet.
Bring the cup with fork down from the cabinet, turn around all the way to face the sink.
Put the cup with fork in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with fork in the sink.

high_descs: Walk forward to the stove then turn right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the fork that's in the sink.
Move a half step to your right and look up.
Open the cabinet that's in front of you and put the fork in the orange cup.
Pick up the orange cup.
Move a step left and a half step backwards.
Put the orange cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in it in the sink.
